00e5 tolke kvinner slik? Det skulle jeg gjerne ha vist."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|magasin"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "9dbb15d20b20fc8326b6ad3b02755ab508357a358039571a16ce4a2ac9d469b5"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-05-14T06:53:03.000Z"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12734994.ece/6t0qkm/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Kommentar-Ann-Inger55.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/236b581e59993aded4a7f61dfe2e0ba69f1f22b8.jpg?590ebee5"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Tause professorer i skj\u00f8rt -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "236b581e59993aded4a7f61dfe2e0ba69f1f22b8"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["tankestreif", "Kjerstin Rab\u00e5s"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "tankestreif,Kjerstin Rab\u00e5s"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "magasin"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "kvinner"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "ji\u0159\u00ed kyli\u00e1n"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss", "pluss/magasin"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12734994.ece/6t0qkm/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Kommentar-Ann-Inger55.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Tause professorer i skj\u00f8rt"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "article"}, {"field": "og-url", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/magasin/2016/05/14/Tause-professorer-i-skj%C3%B8rt-12734995.ece"}, {"field": "pageclass", "value": ["article"]}, {"field": "publishtime", "value": "2016-05-14T07:51:17.000Z"}, {"field": "recs-articleid", "value": "12734995"}, {"field": "recs-category-type", "value": "taxonomy"}, {"field": 